{
  "stem": "22979.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to go to the bathroom. 10 o'clock was [NON-ENGLISH] And you had to go back to your dormitory, to your little place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was Babylon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody pushed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody screamed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So finally, I get to the water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I hardly made it at 10 o'clock back to my dormitory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But still, it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were crying, shivering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And finally, somehow, we went to sleep. 4 o'clock in the morning, screaming, [NON-ENGLISH], knocking on every bed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we had to rush out for say appell, for roll call.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we did that too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then again, the SS and the kapos and all-- we were standing from 4:00 in the morning, until it was good light.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, the SS-- I don't know if it was Drexler, because she was the lagerfuhrer in the SS guard, the SS lagerfuhrer-- and Fraulein Drexler.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, after, you know, maybe it was already close to dawn, we didn't get to eat nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Only later, they brought kettle with water, little, lukewarm, dark water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- so we got a little tea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't recall if I got it or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But then they separated 50 from the 1,000-- 999.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the middle again, between the two barracks, they built a tent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the 50 of us had to line up, one by one, still in our civilian clothes, and marching into the tent.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "On the side-- the right side of the tent were SS women in uniforms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So one by one, [NON-ENGLISH]-- undress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Everything undress, but you know, in the bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we undressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the last women-- a little while-- examined us, you know, if we are not hiding anything-- you know, nude.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A gynecology-- or I don't know-- examined us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they shaved us, our hair everywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
